<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Verify Your Email — Ibibina System</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: #f4f6f8;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        background: #1a3c5e;
        padding: 32px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      .body {
        padding: 40px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .body h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #1a3c5e;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 24px 0;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        background: #1a3c5e;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .token-box {
        background: #f0f4f8;
        border: 1px solid #d1dce8;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        word-break: break-all;
        color: #1a3c5e;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f4f6f8;
        padding: 20px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='wrapper'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Ibibina System</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='body'>
        <h2>Hello, {{name}}!</h2>
        <p>You have requested to verify your email address for your administrator account.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to complete verification. This link expires in
          <strong>24 hours</strong>.</p>
        <a href='{{verificationUrl}}' class='btn'>Verify Email Address</a>
        <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
        <div class='token-box'>{{verificationUrl}}</div>
        <p>If you did not request this verification, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        &copy;
        {{year}}
        Ibibina System &mdash; This is an automated message, please do not reply.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>